Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.75,0:01:37.76,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,950)\pos(490,478)\fsp5\blur2}迷惑的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子 不想受傷就退下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你們帶走他的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是受傷這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小命可不保哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多重影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法.五月雨血河
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我施展的可不是忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:02:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是殺人術
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李 你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 怎麼沒看到鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都平安無事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不過沒看到轟隊長的蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納命來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 放開我 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:03:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你回到同伴身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟 丸鐵 你們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和小櫻 濃眉他們也走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的任務是押送他去京城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是整條船都沉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幾個傢伙居然追上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其讓那些不忍帶走他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如就地正法算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就地正法 什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正押送到京城也是死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私下行刑總比放跑他強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能不能逃跑還不一定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任務是押送這傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就讓你立刻人頭落地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡應該沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們好像迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們好像來到森林的最深處了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以通過月亮辨認方向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在回河邊會有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們索性直接穿過森林去京城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務還是要執行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才不是說要把這傢伙就地正法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是最壞的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道小櫻他們現在怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑鳴人的實力 絕對不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們趕快去找鳴人會合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:08:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種奇怪的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們追
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許鳴人在他們手上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是向著月亮走的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮怎麼跑到身後了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷惑的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦進入 就再也出不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是被押送的囚犯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒資格說話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這個迷惑的森林 你知道些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事 快說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不忍的老窩就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我們在不忍的勢力範圍押送你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個森林最適合做為老窩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濃霧 突然吹起的狂風 強烈的磁場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都能打亂人們的方向感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次進來的人絕對無法出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們豈不是走不出森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你們來說是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不忍的成員 所以另當別論
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我帶你們離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 你是不忍 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就像你家的院子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 麻煩你帶路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是傻瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以剛才那些不忍的身手來看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承認這裡就像你們家的院子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也相信不忍的老窩就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還搞不清楚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會假裝穿越森林
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後帶我們去他們的老窩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在事態緊急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不死 我們就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種惡貫滿盈的人 死有餘辜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傷是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偷了不忍搶來的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現後 遭到他們嚴刑拷打
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幾個不忍並非救我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是想找回那些錢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們拿到錢後 就會殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我會相信你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不忍的老窩就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不忍就佔有地利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們闖進不忍的院子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管丸鐵是否背叛他們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都可能被其他不忍攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我們現在的處境
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能相信他的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 非常順利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走這條小路他們很難發現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙真的值得信任嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就習慣這種蛇的毒性了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上當了 你們上當了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法.土石翻身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上當的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是影分身和變身術的組合
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我怎麼殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少做夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 打算趁機逃跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你出手相助 丸鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這架勢 想動手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為騙得了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟著丸鐵走 就能全身而退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 轟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任務可是押送丸鐵去京城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人我無法原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家人以及弟弟 都被他殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸鐵…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算丸鐵是那群壞蛋的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.99,0:22:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你這樣復仇又能得到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是押送丸鐵去京城嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我覺得丸鐵不像壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 如果你非要殺他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:22:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別怪我不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:22:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時我只能用武力阻止你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.88,0:23:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰的記憶
